-- Syntax for this file here: https://github.com/yesodweb/persistent/blob/master/docs/Persistent-entity-syntax.md

User
    ident Text
    password Text
    fullname Text Maybe
    createdAt UTCTime
    UniqueUser ident
    deriving Typeable
    deriving Show

WeatherQuery
    username String
    city String
    weatherInfo String
    createdAt UTCTime
    deriving Show

